{"tid":1482233,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"一家三口，由邊度出發好","createTime":"2019-08-18T04:33:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T04:44:37.000Z","uid":174775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a50ddc782d193c8dae13fa3b0c6c675c6519db45","tid":1482233,"uid":174775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:33:29.000Z","msg":"小朋友15個月，&ldquo;咩&ldquo;帶&ldquo;咩&rdquo;住行，想行兩個鐘左右就走，係維園出發好定邊度中途加入？"},{"pid":"ef79dfe1a9f288928738b9eaa4066d2bec670512","tid":1482233,"uid":131842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:34:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇埋地圖了解情況 <a href=\"https://hkmap.live\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkmap.live&d=MqHS405OUPR0rJ167hdmPNmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=768430cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkmap.live</a></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Sq2pFt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Sq2pFt.png&h=8b87fcf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[長期置頂] [iOS/Android/PC/Mac] 香城online正式加入地圖功能<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438115\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438115</a>"},{"pid":"220c151a62a892a132ae465127b333131148cee5","tid":1482233,"uid":139409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:34:41.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【英重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bnf9O7G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbnf9O7G.jpg&h=5ee9af01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n// 英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）//<br />\n<br />\n👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 就打0852<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=MqHS405OUPR0rJ167hdmPNmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=f2fe9f7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\nQ: 簽咗咁多聯署 / 英國佬唔會幫我地 / 英國佬講咗咁耐都冇做過嘢簽嚟都冇用<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗1分鐘搞掂又冇成本嘅嘢點解唔做咗先 <br />\n<br />\n六合彩咁難中你又買<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n今次係有下議會議員帶頭講要俾full citizenship BNO holder<br />\n10萬人都簽唔到叫人地點幫你啊<br />\n我地要送子彈啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n🔥⭐️Q: 好多97後都冇BNO 我地唔可以扔低佢地⭐️🔥<br />\n<br />\nA: 有BC又有幾多人會即刻走 <br />\n反而有咗後路可以更盡情咁去抗爭<br />\n同埋到時大量英國國民喺香港 可以增加英國嘅談判籌碼<br />\n真係去到最壞情況都可以諗方法帶埋d細路走<br />\n<br />\nQ: 佢要tick Only British citizens or UK residents have the right to sign<br />\n我 得 / 冇BNO簽唔簽得？<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗verify citizenship 自己諗簽唔簽<br />\n只要提供 email address + 英文名 ＋選Location + Postal code<br />\n<br />\nQ: Postal code 打咩好？<br />\n<br />\nA: 記住喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 成功例子參考<br />\n852 <br />\n0852 <br />\n00000 <br />\n000000<br />\n<br />\n再貼多次條Link:<br />\n<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=MqHS405OUPR0rJ167hdmPNmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=f2fe9f7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"48d52261c206793053fd4d33fb5ebe8962981e20","tid":1482233,"uid":201656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:34:50.000Z","msg":"炮台山"},{"pid":"10cad917565de67120274016b74adf6149e904f9","tid":1482233,"uid":281567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"